          OUR <span class="text-pink-600">AMAZING WORK</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600">
          Explore real projects we’ve brought to life.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Portfolio Grid -->
      <div id="portfolio-grid" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-10">
