        categoryColor="blue-600"
        borderColor="blue-500/30"
        title="LINKPOD"
        description="LINKPOD is a 2-in-1 Magnetic MiFi Router Pouch + Phone Integration Stand System designed to unify portable connectivity into one compact experience. It transforms the MiFi router from a loose, forgotten device into a structured companion to your phone."
        partnerLabel="Product Development, Product Design"
        partnerName="Ndinga Dyongo"
        animationDelay="0s"
        data-tags="Invent, Product development, Product design, mifi-router, mifi-router attachment."
      />
        
             <!-- Example Card 2 -->
      <PortfolioCard
        href="case-studies/nogqaza-case-study.html"
        imageSrc="/images/electro-fix-logo-designed-by-reserved-designs.avif"
        imageAlt="Nogqaza A fast reflex Xhosa game by reserved designs."
        category="Digitized Childhood Game"
        categoryColor="pink-600"
        borderColor="pink-500/30"
        title="NOGQAZA"
        description="Never lose your sharpest self to passive scrolling. This NOGQAZA version revives a classic Xhosa childhood reflex game — the one played by tearing pages from school exercise books, writing numbers 1–12, and racing to tap them in order as fast as possible. A digitised childhood classic — rebuilt to demand active attention in an age of effortless answers. No AI assistance. No passive scrolling. Just pure, active human thinking under pressure."
        partnerLabel="Website, Logo"
        partnerName="Reserved Designs"
        animationDelay="0.1s"
        data-tags="Website Design & Development, Branding, Logo Design, web design."
      />

        <PortfolioCard
          href="case-studies/anti-qr-fraud-casestudy.html"
          imageSrc="/images/achievers-academy-logo-revamp-by-reserved-designs.svg"
          imageAlt="Qr-code payment security with anti-overlay design from reserved designs"
          category="QR-Code payment security"
          categoryColor="blue-600"
          borderColor="blue-500/30"
          title="ANTI-QR CODE OVERLAY FRAUD"
          description="Across South Africa and globally, QR-based payments have rapidly become a preferred transaction method. Platforms like SnapScan and Zapper have enabled businesses to move faster, reduce friction, and operate without cash or card dependency. But within this speed lies a critical vulnerability, the physical display itself. A physical security system that eliminates QR overlay fraud at the point of interaction without software, training, or behaviour change. Anti-QR Overlay Fraud Display Technology secures the last inch of every cashless transaction. Five physical innovations working together to make overlay attacks visually obvious and practically impossible."
          partnerLabel="payment security, card-less transaction protection, QR-code base fraud"
          partnerName="Reserved Designs"
          data-tags="payment security, card-less transaction security, QR-code base fraud"
        />

